description.en: Million is a decentralized digital currency pegged to a minimum value of $1.00 USD with a fixed-supply of 1,000,000 tokens, for a total market cap of $1,000,000+ USD. Million was founded by TechLead, an ex-Google / ex-Facebook tech lead with over 1,000,000 subscribers on YouTube (as a millionaire).
